{"tid":1860325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野狼Disco原作者正式向寶石Gem發律師信","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T07:22:11.000Z","uid":89543,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"15d4cebf562863ba238ba7a8e78e1481a2704f9f","tid":1860325,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wwolfdisco.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2Fwwolfdisco.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830&h=e23d328b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《野狼Disco》嘅「Beat」係芬蘭音樂製作人Vilho Ihaksi製作嘅作品《More Sun》。Ihaksi經常喺youtube發表佢製作嘅音樂。<br />\n<br />\n而佢嘅作品係可以免費使用嘅，但就寫到明係「非商用」同埋要落返佢個名：「Feel free to use it non-commercially (no monetization), but remember to write &quot;Ihaksi&quot; on the credits!」。<span style=\"color: red;\">而《野狼disco》嘅官方MV就寫作詞作曲都係寶石Gem，完全無寫到Ihaksi嘅名。</span><br />\n<br />\n《More Sun》作者Vilho Ihaksi同版權方瑪西瑪國際Maxima International Media委託咗微博用戶「唱片老趙」，代表作者同版權方向《野狼Disco》相關利益方發送正式律師函。維護返作者應有嘅權益。<span style=\"color: red;\">當中指出《野狼Disco》嘅商演、廣告、春晚，作者幾乎都係最後先知。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/640.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F640.jpeg&h=207c048c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aff5a95dd86ea480f9432b755ce4c4292469070d","tid":1860325,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcc04d37b0e685ef474dd08163523b65cba6765","tid":1860325,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"野狼disco?乜撚野黎？"},{"pid":"305d8d9f510cfd49d1b8e2d658bb364be4d6f4dc","tid":1860325,"uid":12008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:56